{"tid":1017008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2男性侵12歲男孩後割喉肢解　葉門公開槍決引百人圍觀「手機狂拍」","createTime":"2019-02-11T07:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T21:14:00.000Z","uid":212399,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4780d18d571467890fec83864ea825af3937d0","tid":1017008,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/3888515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2F3888515.jpg&h=6c30f09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 執法人員將槍口抵在死刑犯背上。（圖／路透社）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n數百名葉門民眾於7日聚集在港口城市亞丁（Aden），在廣場上圍成一圈、高聲喧鬧。人群的中心是2名將被處決的死刑犯，他們2018年因在公共場合綁架、性侵並殺害一名12歲男孩被定罪。當執法人員舉起槍，人們也紛紛舉起手機，錄下公開行刑的畫面。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》報導，28歲的里法特（Wadah Refat）和31歲的卡利（Mohamed Khaled）在2018年5月性侵並謀殺名為薩阿德（Mohamed Saad）的12歲男孩。案發當時，薩阿德在其中一名歹徒家附近玩耍，沒想到2人突然出現，將他拖進家中性侵得逞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/3888518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2F3888518.jpg&h=f735e54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼ 民眾聚集圍觀；執法人員在行刑前餵死刑犯喝水。（圖／路透社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/3888517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2F3888517.jpg&h=2e15f7e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據西班牙《世界報》取得的法庭文件，薩阿德遭到性侵後不斷哭喊、乞求幫助；里法特和卡利無法讓他安靜下來，其中一人便抓起一把刀，割斷他的喉嚨，因此被判處死刑。據悉，還有一名33歲婦女因幫助2名歹徒分屍而被判死刑，但行刑日因懷孕而延後。<br />\n《每日郵報》指出，葉門是全世界人均死刑率最高的國家之一，而槍決是最常見的方法。伊斯蘭教法是葉門所有法律的立法來源，犯下謀殺、性侵和恐怖主義犯罪者最高可判處死刑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190211/1375229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190211%2F1375229.htm&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1xmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=84e5663b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190211/1375229.htm</a>"},{"pid":"515ca623b92eb7bacda8e660a1bd93c723fa742d","tid":1017008,"uid":201604,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"也門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577806ce121344192ef3ca2a8773dac47e37706c","tid":1017008,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53bbd56b471a62f47aba513555493fa0ef7676d","tid":1017008,"uid":39177,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"個未出世ge bb係咪傳說中ge惡魔之子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d81efaec47ffce9b7e16dc9c8f2823e72004492","tid":1017008,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ddec941ea7b8b257014d275a5ba32056d56cf9","tid":1017008,"uid":25345,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/239/49d/23949df3d30dd61fb833a45e8c24661867fe894e_n.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F239%2F49d%2F23949df3d30dd61fb833a45e8c24661867fe894e_n.JPG&h=7f5f78ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d02da31842ec0ab4bb86804a54ce1074feb38c8","tid":1017008,"uid":9526,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"點解要餵水先槍決 有冇人知?<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解唔拎支槍隊住佢個口再射"},{"pid":"8977af72c9b55dc73d9bcdcbf6587cc14e11f460","tid":1017008,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據悉，還有一名33歲婦女因幫助2名歹徒分屍而被判死刑，但行刑日因懷孕而延後。</blockquote><br />\n一直keep著大肚就無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cf1fdc9cd3badb9bca5d5a638e10d2377f601c","tid":1017008,"uid":170229,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0